7181873622645001514.desc: I normally don’t show this side of myself, as my goal for this TikTok page is to make light of my circumstances. But I also want to be transparent with you all, and also show that living with this challenge is not always sunshine and rainbows. Living with 50+ food allergies takes a toll on my mental health, and some days are more difficult than others. Its okay to have moments were you need to cry it out, and vent. If you have food allergies too, I know it can feel super lonely, but i promise you’re not alone. ❤️
7181873622645001514.author: theallergicgirl
